This paper deals with conceptual database design and functional dependencies, which are core topics in the field of databases (cs.DB). It also addresses the issue of incomplete information, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper uses mathematical formalism and logic, which are also relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and cryptography (cs.CR). Finally, the paper discusses properties of FDs, which are related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
